Customer Insights Dashboard using Tableau

Charles A. Hulebak

Project Overview

This project utilized Consumer Financial Protection Bureau (CFPB) data associated with consumer complaints.

There were over 350,000 complaints tracked between 2011 and 2015, which were categorized by various characteristics ranging from products, issues, location, date, and more.

This was a lengthy project that required data preprocessing, including cleansing, organization, and filtering. Once this was performed, several prototypes were developed as dashboards to quickly obtain specific information within the content of the data.

Tableau provided a convenient way to create specific sheets, then compose the final dashboard with the respective information.

The dashboard may be quickly viewed within the Tableau Public website at: https://public.tableau.com/views/CI_Dashboard/Dashboard1?:language=en&:display_count=y&publish=yes&:origin=viz_share_link.

The dashboard is also embedded within the content, however it must load a large file; the initial link provided is recommended for quickly viewing.
